          "1": "Ensuring the accuracy of information provided",
          "2": "Complying with all applicable laws and regulations"
        }
      },
      "intellectualProperty": {
        "title": "Intellectual Property",
        "content": "All content, trademarks, and intellectual property on this platform are owned by Mert CIN Certificate Authorisation or its licensors. Unauthorized use is prohibited."
      },
      "limitation": {
        "title": "Limitation of Liability",
        "content": "We strive to provide accurate and reliable services, but we cannot guarantee uninterrupted or error-free operation. Our liability is limited to the maximum extent permitted by law."
      },
      "contact": {
        "title": "Contact Information",
        "content": "For questions about these Terms of Use, please contact us at"
      }
    }
  },
  "kvkk": {
    "title": "GDPR Notice",
    "lastUpdated": "Last Updated",
    "sections": {
      "intro": {
        "title": "Introduction",
        "content": "This notice explains how we process your personal data in accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and other applicable data protection laws."
      },
      "dataController": {
        "title": "Data Controller",
        "content": "Mert CIN Certificate Authorisation is the data controller responsible for your personal data. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring compliance with data protection regulations."
      },
      "personalData": {
        "title": "Personal Data We Process",
        "content": "We process the following categories of personal data:",
        "items": {
          "0": "Identity data (name, surname, national ID number)",
          "1": "Contact data (email address, phone number, address)",
          "2": "Certificate and training records",
          "3": "Technical data (IP address, login data, usage information)"
        }
      },
      "processingPurpose": {
        "title": "Purpose of Processing",
        "content": "Your personal data is processed for certificate issuance and verification, service provision, legal compliance, and platform improvement. We only process data for legitimate purposes with appropriate legal basis."
      },
      "dataSubjectRights": {
        "title": "Your Rights as a Data Subject",
        "content": "Under GDPR, you have the following rights:",
        "items": {
          "0": "Right to access your personal data",
          "1": "Right to rectification of inaccurate data",
          "2": "Right to erasure (right to be forgotten)",
          "3": "Right to restriction of processing",
          "4": "Right to data portability"
        }
      },
      "contact": {
        "title": "Contact",
        "content": "To exercise your rights or for any questions regarding data processing, please contact us at"
      }
    }
  },
  "howItWorks": {
    "title": "How It Works",
    "subtitle": "Discover how our platform simplifies certificate management for educational institutions",
    "processTitle": "Simple 4-Step Process",
    "processSubtitle": "From registration to reporting, everything you need in one platform",
    "steps": {
      "registration": {
        "title": "Institution Registration",
        "description": "Create your institutional account in minutes. Provide your organization details and get verified by our team to start issuing certificates."
      },
      "createCertificate": {
        "title": "Create Certificates",
        "description": "Design and issue digital certificates using our intuitive interface. Bulk upload student data, customize templates, and generate certificates instantly."
      },
      "verification": {
        "title": "Instant Verification",
        "description": "Recipients and employers can verify certificates in seconds using TCKN or certificate number. All verifications are logged and tracked for security."
      },
      "reporting": {
        "title": "Analytics & Reporting",
        "description": "Access detailed reports on certificate issuance, verification requests, and student data. Export reports and track your institution's performance."
      }
    },
